  "texts": [
    "We then content analyze pre-intervention videos produced by individuals included in our sampling frame to provide a sense of how much EBMHC content already existed on the TikTok platform, prior to our interventions (RQ1).",
    "After that, we compare change in pre-to post-intervention content production in order to assess the effectiveness of our interventions in changing content production behavior (RQ2); i.e., our ability to \"influence the influencers. \"",
    "Note that the influencers involved in our study had a large \"reach\" (i.e., follower count) on the TikTok platform.",
    "Control group influencers totaled approximately 8.4 million followers at the onset of data collection, while those enrolled in the treatment groups totaled 8.5 million followers (cumulative reach = 16.9 million).",
    "Thus, we believe that changes in influencer content-producing behavior have the opportunity to reach many users on the TikTok platform."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}